♪ I'm not expecting any light
at your door ♪

1086
01:03:06,554 --> 01:03:08,139
♪ There's nothing left ♪

1087
01:03:08,223 --> 01:03:14,354
♪ Just the pieces of everything
we could have been before ♪

1088
01:03:14,437 --> 01:03:18,733
♪ Evermore ♪

1089
